    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator that applies a momentary kick to overcome static friction. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>When starting from stop or changing direction, a power pulse is applied for a short duration to overcome inertia and static friction.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Motor</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base motor class (must implement <ref refid="classevam_1_1_kick_decor_1a21a827853209051b250d1d16b1235d3d" kindref="member">Go(signed short)</ref>) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kKickDuration</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Kick pulse duration in milliseconds. Default: 20ms. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kKickPower</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Kick power. Range: -1000..1000. Default: 1000 (full power). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
